  "description": "A rhythmic deep membrane: fast reactivity to snap to sub-bass kicks, but selectivity and memory tuned so that each hit reads as a distinct pressure event rather than a sustained tone. Medium permeability keeps the coupling signal punchy. The membrane surfaces briefly with each low-frequency transient, then sinks back. Like pressure waves felt through water.",
